Package APproject

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    Admin class extends Person and is used to create an Admin who knows about the all the rooms of the college and and excepts or rejects the requests made by students to book a room.
    Booked_rooms
    This class is used to create an object whenever a request of a student is accepted by Admin or either an Admin or a Faculty books a room
    Courses
    Courses class is used to create a new course.
    courses_view
    An adapter class to convert Courses type Objects and to a type that can be displayed in combobox
    Credentials  
    Faculty
    Faculty class extends Person and is used to create a Faculty who knows about the all the rooms and can book a room by checking the room availability
    Main
    Main Class is usedd to instantiate the project, it creates the GUI pages and creates instance of the Management class.
    Management
    Management knows everything about the all the rooms, all courses , all users i.e.
    Person
    An abstract that is used to denote the user.
    Request
    This class object is used to store the information of any request that is being made by any student
    Room
    A class whose object is used to Store all the information of a room.
    Student
    Student class extends Person and is used to create a Student who can check available rooms at a particular time slot and then can make a request for a room.
    TimeTable
    A timetable object is used to store the information of all the courses.
